Brothers and Sisters in Christ, I‚Äôm @Shooglenifty. God is good and His mercy endures forever!
***By posting you are agreeing to our posting standards. We will remove a post according to our interpretation (written by us) of the guidelines below. If there is any confusion, please DM.
***My hopes for the group is to foster phileo between the Christian diaspora that has chosen to join this group. We want to be a place where unbelievers come for answers and believers come to be bolstered in their faith. By the grace of God through the blood of Jesus we will bring His love to multitudes. My reasoning? I believe this: "Never doubt God‚Äôs mighty power to work in you and accomplish all this. He will achieve infinitely more than your greatest request, your most unbelievable dream, and exceed your wildest imagination! He will outdo them all, for his miraculous power constantly energizes you.‚Äù Ephesians 3:20 TPT

***PLEASE READ BEFORE POSTING: Posts that are encouraged (think ENGAGEMENT! and WHAT IS GOD TELLING YOU!):

1. Testimonies, praise reports, prayer requests, encouragements, prophecies, words from God, exhortations, etc.

2. Questions of those looking to our community for answers that only God can give.

3. Sermons, articles, videos, pictures and verses as long as they have a good description outlining who, what, where, why and how. If you don't respect the link you are posting or the other Christians in the group enough to take some time with your post, please don't post it. 

***It seems most just post and run (seagull posting) and this is not God's heart nor mine. This group has ONE timeline. It also has many members. Is it respectful on your part to post several one-line posts in a row pushing someone else's well-thought post or plea out of sight of the group? 

With that in mind the following types of posts will be removed at the sole discretion of the moderators:
1. Off-topic posts: politics, flat earth, begging for followers or money (please reach out to the admin if you believe you have a worthy fundraising cause. You will be required to provide proof and cause. Any fundraiser posted without prior discussion will be removed), promoting personal agendas, etc.

2. Intentionally divisive, argumentative, disrespectful or racist posts.

3. Low effort (Just posting a video/link is not sufficient within the group, you must also write YOUR OWN description of the link/video; the included video/link description is not acceptable) or multiple posts in a row (limit of 2 posts per 3 hours)

4. Posts that don't meet the criteria mentioned above

5. Any reposts from other groups that are unrelated to Christianity; reposts of posts already in the group timeline (if you agree with a post just say it in the original post); and any reposts of your disagreements within a post brought to the group timeline.

6. Anyone who spams the same post to multiple groups (yes, I check timelines), or continually posts the same post/s in the timeline. 

7. All members who block the administrators and moderators will be removed.

***Remember that we are the body of Christ. Please keep your posts in line with Philippians 4:8 (ESV): Finally, brothers, whatever is true, whatever is honorable, whatever is just, whatever is pure, whatever is lovely, whatever is commendable, if there is any excellence, if there is anything worthy of praise, think (post!) about these things.

***‚ÄúThe Lord bless you and keep you; the Lord make his face to shine upon you and be gracious to you; the Lord lift up his countenance upon you and give you peace. ‚ÄúSo shall they put my name upon the people of Israel, and I will bless them.‚Äù Numbers 6:24-27 ESV

***Group Creator:  @Micaiah
Admins/Mods: @Shooglenifty, @riustan

This son of a bitch don't even know who you are just like I don't. I'm not going to assume to know. Fucking fake Internet psychic. And then he has a whole rigid set of laws that he's created as to who can and cannot be real veterans. Go fuck yourself Eric whatever the fuck. My guess is you were a national guardsman in the rear with the gear or never even stepped foot in a hostile nation. My guess is you aren't even a combat veteran. Yeah you're on here trying to act like some badass arbiter of all that is being a veteran. Get bent you son of a bitch.

Time to get down to bidness and compel some folks to do some ‚Äòsplainin‚Äô under oath. You don‚Äôt know for sure who will be chair exactly of which congressional committee, but there will be several of them running at the same time, looking to shake out some verifiable truth from the dumpster of misrule, sedition, and perfidy that America fell into the past decade. Here are a couple of my top outlines for inquiries.     Covid-19. Forget about Fauci for the moment. Then put Dr. Fauci‚Äôs ass in the witness chair and wring out the ‚Äòsplainin.‚Äô Ask about the patents on the various parts of C-19 and on the mRNA ‚Äúvaccines‚Äù cooked up to fight it, and who got the royalties emanating off all of that. Ask him how he continued gain-of-function research post-2014 after the White House directed it to stop. Ask him to ‚Äòsplain‚Äô his relations with one Peter Daszak of the EcoHealth Alliance.     Ask Deborah Birx to ‚Äòsplain‚Äô exactly what was going on in that White House C-19 task force. Why did the public health officers demonize early treatments with known, safe, drugs and censor anyone who spoke out against their insane policies. What did the task force know about Pfizer and Moderna‚Äôs ‚Äúvaccine‚Äù trials. Ask Rochelle Walensky how come she and the CDC kept pushing mRNA shots and boosters long after a broad array of injuries and deaths presented from their use. Put Bill Gates‚Äôs ass in the chair and have him ‚Äòsplain‚Äô the labyrinth of funding mechanisms he set up to push ‚Äúvaccines‚Äù all over the globe and how his tentacles happen to penetrate into the World Health Org (WHO). Time for FBI Director Christopher Wray to ‚Äòsplain‚Äô how come he sat silently in possession of the Hunter Biden laptop ‚Äî stuffed as it was with deal memoranda about payoffs from Ukraine and other foreign lands ‚Äî through the first impeachment of Mr. Trump in late 2019 and early 2020, from the initial House hearings through the Senate trail‚Ä¶ when said laptop was full of exculpatory evidence proving that Mr. Trump had a good reason to inquire about those matters in a phone call with V. Zelensky. Ask Mr. Wray how many federal agents were involved in the January 6 riot at the Capitol building, both inside and outside. Don‚Äôt let him bullshit the committee about ‚Äúongoing investigations‚Äù blah blah. Ask Mr. Wray if he directly ordered his agents to monitor and censor social media companies, and, if not him, who did?[...]      Find a special booster chair for Merrick Garland to ‚Äòsplain‚Äô how come so many January 6 suspects are being held indefinitely pre-trial in the DC lockup on rinky-dink charges under the harshest conditions (solitary confinement, denial of medical care) in defiance of due process of law, in particular the constitutional right to a speedy trial. Ask Mr. Garland why he‚Äôs devoting vast resources of the DOJ to pursue ever more January 6 protesters on rinky-dink charges. Ask him to ‚Äòsplain‚Äô how it came to pass that he went after parents protesting at school boards about indecent sex ed for little children and racist anti-white indoctrination. Ask him about sending SWAT teams on predawn raids to the homes of investigation targets whose lawyers volunteered to deliver them to the FBI offices. Ask him why he appointed a RussiaGate-involved lawyer, one Robert K Hur, as Special Counsel in the ‚ÄúJoe Biden‚Äù classified document matter.[...]    One somewhat disconnected thought, a sort-of postscript: The World Economic Forum‚Äôs annual jamboree at Davos, Switzerland, opens this coming Monday. Der Schwabenklaus, Bill Gates, and an international cast of global Big Machers will be in one room for the opening plenary session all at the same time. Think about it. Just sayin‚Äô."
